00:27:00,468 --> 00:27:02,968
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Semakin aku mendengar kalian,
makin aneh jadinya.</i></font>

349
00:27:02,968 --> 00:27:06,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau juga beli barang-barang tambahan,
seperti buket dan sepatu pernikahan.</font>

350
00:27:06,168 --> 00:27:08,577
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi aku akan mengurangi biaya
sewamu bulan depan.</font>

351
00:27:09,837 --> 00:27:11,038
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

352
00:27:20,948 --> 00:27:22,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari ini?</font>

353
00:27:22,887 --> 00:27:24,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak bisa. Aku harus kerja malam ini.</font>

354
00:27:29,097 --> 00:27:31,627
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Terus kalian turun di gedung pernikahan
tempatku bekerja.</i></font>

355
00:27:33,827 --> 00:27:37,337
<font color=#FFFF00>Bok Nam-ssi, bisa kaurapikan
ruang tunggu pengantinnya?</font>

356
00:27:37,337 --> 00:27:38,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

357
00:27:39,367 --> 00:27:40,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi.</font>

358
00:27:41,478 --> 00:27:42,577
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

359
00:27:55,958 --> 00:27:57,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf./
Ya.</font>

360
00:28:04,797 --> 00:28:06,228
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jadi begitulah perkiraanku...</i></font>

361
00:28:06,228 --> 00:28:08,768
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...kalian berdua bukan seperti
pasangan biasanya.</i></font>

362
00:28:09,067 --> 00:28:11,137
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jadi kukira kalian terlibat
semacam pernikahan kontrak.</i></font>

363
00:28:11,538 --> 00:28:12,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Selesai.</font>

364
00:28:13,907 --> 00:28:15,637
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

365
00:28:19,307 --> 00:28:21,107
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih, Bo Mi-nim.</font>

366
00:28:21,347 --> 00:28:22,617
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih banyak.</font>

367
00:28:22,617 --> 00:28:24,547
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tidak foto sekali lagi?/
Apa?</font>

368
00:28:25,617 --> 00:28:28,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami membingkai satu foto gratis.</font>

369
00:28:28,617 --> 00:28:30,887
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tidak foto sekali lagi saja?</font>

370
00:28:30,887 --> 00:28:31,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak perlu.</font>

371
00:28:31,958 --> 00:28:33,458
<font color=#FFFF00>Serius, gratis? Kalau begitu, baiklah.</font>

372
00:28:33,458 --> 00:28:34,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Balik ke posisi tadi.</font>

373
00:28:42,567 --> 00:28:45,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukannya kalian harus berpose sedikit?</font>

374
00:28:45,337 --> 00:28:47,538
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian sepertinya tidak
saling dekat.</font>

375
00:28:47,538 --> 00:28:48,678
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa iya?</font>

376
00:28:49,107 --> 00:28:51,208
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Hee-nim, coba pose lain.</font>

377
00:28:52,448 --> 00:28:53,877
<font color=#FFFF00>Pose lain?</font>

378
00:28:53,877 --> 00:28:55,047
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa menciumnya.</font>

379
00:28:55,047 --> 00:28:56,147
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?/
Apa?</font>

380
00:28:56,478 --> 00:28:58,647
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau kau bisa melingkarkan lenganmu
di pinggangnya.</font>

381
00:28:59,288 --> 00:29:00,887
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini 'kan foto pernikahan.</font>

382
00:29:01,147 --> 00:29:02,587
<font color=#FFFF00>Jepretan fotomu payah sekali.</font>

383
00:29:03,188 --> 00:29:06,887
<font color=#FFFF00>Nanti kau yang disalahkan selamanya,
kalau fotonya jelek.</font>

384
00:29:08,728 --> 00:29:11,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian dua, coba pose lain.</font>

385
00:29:12,367 --> 00:29:14,938
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian berdua setidaknya bersentuhan
atau apa lah.</font>

386
00:29:24,307 --> 00:29:26,008
<font color=#FFFF00>Oke.</font>

387
00:29:26,448 --> 00:29:28,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bisa juga, 'kan?</font>

388
00:29:29,518 --> 00:29:32,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Berjabat tangan juga bisa menjadi
tanda saling bersentuhan.</font>

389
00:29:32,587 --> 00:29:33,847
<font color=#FFFF00>Kufoto, ya.</font>

390
00:29:39,827 --> 00:29:42,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Terus tanda tanganku, kau
tahu darimana?</font>

391
00:29:42,428 --> 00:29:45,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tanda tangan, waktu bayar
sewa gedung pernikahan.</font>

392
00:29:45,867 --> 00:29:47,627
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Nam Se Hee]</i></font>

393
00:29:48,867 --> 00:29:49,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar juga.</font>

394
00:29:50,867 --> 00:29:54,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Terus kunci inggris (spanner) itu?</font>

395
00:30:15,528 --> 00:30:19,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku itu mau buka birmu.
'Kan waktu itu tak ada pembuka botol.</font>

396
00:30:20,567 --> 00:30:24,538
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kalian tidak minum saja sekarang,
pasangan suami istri palsu?</font>

397
00:30:25,107 --> 00:30:27,837
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan, apa aku harus memanggil
kalian penuduh saja?</font>

398
00:30:40,988 --> 00:30:44,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan juga, besok, aku mau
minta ganti rugi.</font>

399
00:30:46,988 --> 00:30:48,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Motor...</font>

400
00:31:01,807 --> 00:31:04,678
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf. Bok Nam-gun.</font>

401
00:31:06,008 --> 00:31:07,107
<font color=#FFFF00>Bok Nam-ssi.</font>

402
00:31:07,678 --> 00:31:09,678
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan. Tuan.</font>

403
00:31:12,918 --> 00:31:14,117
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa aku bicara sebentar?</font>

404
00:31:18,528 --> 00:31:21,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau datang cepat hari ini.
Kau shift pagi hari ini?</font>

405
00:31:21,657 --> 00:31:23,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku butuh hari-hari yang seperti ini.</font>

406
00:31:27,827 --> 00:31:29,438
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau mau ikut kumpul-kumpul hari ini?</i></font>

407
00:31:29,738 --> 00:31:30,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumpul-kumpul?</font>

408
00:31:33,708 --> 00:31:35,238
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Maksudmu sama teman sekelas SMA?</i></font>

409
00:31:35,238 --> 00:31:36,538
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tentu, aku pasti ikut.</i></font>

410
00:31:36,607 --> 00:31:38,748
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bukankah kita sekalian ambil
kartu undangan pernikahan Su Jin juga?</i></font>

411
00:31:39,008 --> 00:31:41,008
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ya./
Si Ji Ho?</i></font>

412
00:31:41,377 --> 00:31:42,547
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ji Ho juga ikut.</i></font>

413
00:31:43,418 --> 00:31:45,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Unni, kukuku juga, tolong diwarnai.</font>

414
00:31:45,948 --> 00:31:48,117
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak apa?/
Ya. Besok aku libur. Jadi tak apa.</font>

415
00:31:53,627 --> 00:31:55,528
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah datang./
Maaf.</font>

416
00:31:57,228 --> 00:31:59,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf. Kalian pasti lama menunggu, ya?</font>

417
00:31:59,268 --> 00:32:00,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak. Kau kedinginan?</font>

418
00:32:00,698 --> 00:32:03,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi bagaimana? Si Bok Nam kesal sekali?</font>

419
00:32:03,198 --> 00:32:05,238
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa si Se Hee harus menjual rumahnya
buat ganti rugi motornya?</font>

420
00:32:05,238 --> 00:32:07,208
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, jangan bicara terlalu cepat.</font>

421
00:32:08,208 --> 00:32:09,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian sudah mengurusi masalahnya?</font>

422
00:32:10,377 --> 00:32:13,877
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami tidak perlu menjual rumah.</font>

423
00:32:14,547 --> 00:32:17,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami sudah bicara baik-baik sama dia,
dan semuanya baik-baik saja sekarang.</font>

424
00:32:18,518 --> 00:32:22,157
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi ada yang berbeda
dengan motor mahal itu.</font>

425
00:32:23,887 --> 00:32:27,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Walau begitu, tak ada yang rusak
selain spionnya. Kami hanya perlu...</font>

426
00:32:28,928 --> 00:32:30,057
<font color=#FFFF00>...mencicil membayarnya.</font>

427
00:32:31,127 --> 00:32:34,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya perlu bekerja lebih keras karena
itu kafenya Bok Nam.</font>

428
00:32:34,498 --> 00:32:37,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Heol. Siapa yang sangka,
dia anaknya bos kafe?</font>

429
00:32:37,998 --> 00:32:42,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Walau begitu, pandangan kita semakin
jelas tentang suamimu./ Apa?</font>

430
00:32:42,137 --> 00:32:45,407
<font color=#FFFF00>Awalnya kita kira
dia orang yang tidak menghabiskan uang.</font>

431
00:32:45,407 --> 00:32:47,407
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi rupanya dia berani
menendang motor mahal itu.</font>

432
00:32:47,407 --> 00:32:48,678
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sampai tercengang.</font>

433
00:32:49,418 --> 00:32:52,387
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga sedikit tercengang.</font>

434
00:32:52,448 --> 00:32:56,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak mau mengakuinya, tapi
dia suami yang setia, bukan?</font>

435
00:32:57,157 --> 00:33:01,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu baru namanya kekuatan cinta.
Aku tahu pasti kau tak mengerti.</font>

436
00:33:01,127 --> 00:33:02,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak usah cari gara-gara, ya.</font>

437
00:33:02,928 --> 00:33:05,765
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lagi tak niat bercandaan, karena aku
mau ikut kumpul-kumpul konyol ini.</font>

438
00:33:06,297 --> 00:33:07,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumpul-kumpul konyol?</font>

439
00:33:07,498 --> 00:33:09,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga penasaran.</font>

440
00:33:09,297 --> 00:33:11,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu? Kenapa kau
menamainya seperti itu?</font>

441
00:33:11,607 --> 00:33:13,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kita sudah sampai,
pasti kalian tahu.</font>

442
00:33:22,117 --> 00:33:23,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Kosmetik yang kupakai hari ini...</font>

443
00:33:24,377 --> 00:33:27,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Ho, ceritakan tentang pernikahanmu.</font>

444
00:33:27,587 --> 00:33:29,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami sebenarnya sangat sedih.</font>

445
00:33:29,258 --> 00:33:32,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa-bisanya kau tidak cerita sama sekali?</font>

446
00:33:32,188 --> 00:33:34,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf. Aku sangat sibuk.</font>

447
00:33:34,688 --> 00:33:36,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kau tinggal dimana sekarang?</font>

448
00:33:36,857 --> 00:33:39,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Apartemen? Kau sewa apa beli?</font>

449
00:33:40,097 --> 00:33:41,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Kami membelinya.</font>

450
00:33:41,837 --> 00:33:44,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagus sekali./
Gaji suamimu pasti besar.</font>

451
00:33:44,198 --> 00:33:46,538
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami juga mencicil, sebenarnya.</font>

452
00:33:46,538 --> 00:33:49,607
<font color=#FFFF00>Zaman sekarang siapa yang beli rumah,
tak pakai cicilan? Itu bukan apa-apanya.</font>

453
00:33:49,607 --> 00:33:52,347
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami juga dulu sangat bahagia seperti
kalian, saat pertama kali menikah.</font>

454
00:33:52,678 --> 00:33:54,577
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi apa kau senang,
sudah menikah sekarang?</font>

455
00:33:56,147 --> 00:33:57,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Yah...</font>

456
00:34:04,418 --> 00:34:05,887
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa aku senang.</font>

457
00:34:06,688 --> 00:34:08,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau senang akan apanya?</font>

458
00:34:08,458 --> 00:34:10,527
<font color=#FFFF00>Suamiku juga langsung
pulang sehabis kerja...</font>

459
00:34:10,527 --> 00:34:12,427
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan bersenang-senang denganku
selama tahun pertama kami.</font>

460
00:34:13,128 --> 00:34:15,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia mencarimu saat dia pulang?</font>

461
00:34:15,998 --> 00:34:18,608
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Ya.</font>

462
00:34:19,038 --> 00:34:22,177
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia juga begitu.</font>

463
00:34:22,938 --> 00:34:25,407
<font color=#FFFF00>Kucing./
<i>Dia mencariku...</i></font>

464
00:34:25,708 --> 00:34:28,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Kucing./
<i>...dan memanggil namaku.</i></font>

465
00:34:29,048 --> 00:34:30,378
<font color=#FFFF00>Waktu kusapa dia...,</font>

466
00:34:31,847 --> 00:34:33,117
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah pulang?</font>

467
00:34:42,097 --> 00:34:45,798
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dia memelukku erat...</i></font>

468
00:34:46,367 --> 00:34:47,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat malam.</font>

469
00:34:48,637 --> 00:34:51,298
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan mengajakku
ke kamar tidur kami.</i></font>

470
00:34:53,068 --> 00:34:55,637
<font color=#FFFF00>Panas, panas.</font>

471
00:34:56,038 --> 00:34:58,378
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi jangan terlalu dini
hamilnya.</font>

472
00:34:58,507 --> 00:35:01,108
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekalinya kau melahirkan,
habislah sudah.</font>

473
00:35:01,208 --> 00:35:04,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu 'kan kalau kita umur 20an.
Kita sudah terlalu tua sekarang.</font>

474
00:35:04,887 --> 00:35:08,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Menurutku juga, hamil awal
juga lebih baik...</font>

475
00:35:09,217 --> 00:35:12,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kemudian rencanaku memudar,
setelah mengunjungi mertua kami.</font>

476
00:35:13,027 --> 00:35:15,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, walau begitu mereka
pasti jauh lebih baik daripada...</font>

477
00:35:15,898 --> 00:35:17,298
<font color=#FFFF00>...bajingan yang kutemui di kantor.</font>

478
00:35:17,628 --> 00:35:18,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo kita minum dan lupakan saja.</font>

479
00:35:19,768 --> 00:35:21,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Bersulang.</font>

480
00:35:22,338 --> 00:35:24,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Soo Ji, kau masih saja banyak minum?</font>

481
00:35:24,538 --> 00:35:26,108
<font color=#FFFF00>Hebat sekali kau.</font>

482
00:35:27,538 --> 00:35:29,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku dulu mengidam bir waktu hamil...,</font>

483
00:35:29,807 --> 00:35:32,077
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi aku menenangkan diri
dengan menonton iklan bir.</font>

484
00:35:32,177 --> 00:35:34,878
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah itu karena kau cuma ingin lihat
bintang iklannya, si Song Joong Ki saja?</font>

485
00:35:36,248 --> 00:35:39,447
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, sekarang, Park Bo Gum jauh lebih
populer dari Song Joong Ki.</font>

486
00:35:39,447 --> 00:35:42,557
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana gadis lajang sepertimu
paham perasaanku?</font>

487
00:35:42,557 --> 00:35:43,757
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah.</font>

488
00:35:47,327 --> 00:35:48,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa disini ada ruang merokok?</font>

489
00:35:48,927 --> 00:35:51,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda bisa merokok di tempat parkir./
Ya.</font>

490
00:35:52,027 --> 00:35:54,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tanya itu?/
Aku takut didenda...</font>

491
00:35:54,367 --> 00:35:55,398
<font color=#FFFF00>...kalau aku merokok sembarangan.</font>

492
00:35:55,467 --> 00:35:58,307
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya juga. Dendanya 'kan kira-kira
100 ribu.</font>

493
00:36:00,068 --> 00:36:01,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Soo Ji.</font>

494
00:36:01,438 --> 00:36:03,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak ada rencana mau menikah?</font>

495
00:36:04,077 --> 00:36:06,378
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku tidak ada rencana mau menikah.</font>

496
00:36:06,548 --> 00:36:09,478
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kalau keputusanmu berubah,
kau mungkin bisa menikah nanti.</font>

497
00:36:09,717 --> 00:36:12,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, mungkin kalau aku berubah pikiran.</font>

498
00:36:12,918 --> 00:36:16,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, bukankah
kau harusnya berhenti merokok?</font>

499
00:36:17,157 --> 00:36:19,987
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?/
Aku benar, 'kan?</font>

500
00:36:20,228 --> 00:36:23,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau mau melahirkan, kau
harus berhenti merokok...</font>

501
00:36:23,697 --> 00:36:26,128
<font color=#FFFF00>...karena adanya
nikotin di tubuhmu.</font>

502
00:36:26,128 --> 00:36:28,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tidak baik bagi si bayi.</font>

503
00:36:28,597 --> 00:36:31,038
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Betul, betul./
Itu tak baik.</i></font>

504
00:36:31,038 --> 00:36:32,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau lihat itu?/
Apa?</font>

505
00:36:33,038 --> 00:36:35,407
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka.../
Ya, kalau kau mau melahirkan...,</font>

506
00:36:35,407 --> 00:36:36,838
<font color=#FFFF00>...tubuhmu harus dirawat baik-baik.</font>

507
00:36:37,038 --> 00:36:39,708
<font color=#FFFF00>...sangat berisik. Makanya kunamai
kumpul-kumpul konyol.</font>

508
00:36:45,947 --> 00:36:49,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa orang jadi sibuk sekali
saat mereka menikah?</font>

509
00:36:49,588 --> 00:36:50,818
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka menyuruh ini itu.</font>

510
00:36:51,487 --> 00:36:53,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah sebabnya semua orang menikah.</font>

511
00:36:53,527 --> 00:36:57,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagian kehidupan yang paling menyenangkan
itu menyarankan orang ini itu.</font>

512
00:36:59,298 --> 00:37:00,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, Ho Rang.</font>

513
00:37:00,628 --> 00:37:02,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukannya kau sudah makan tadi?</font>

514
00:37:03,168 --> 00:37:04,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau lapar lagi?/
Ya.</font>

515
00:37:05,507 --> 00:37:06,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lapar.</font>

516
00:37:07,608 --> 00:37:10,177
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tadi tidak bisa makan banyak di sana.
Perutku kesal.</font>

517
00:37:10,737 --> 00:37:13,608
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, aku tadi yang adu mulut sama
mereka. Kenapa perutmu yang marah?</font>

518
00:37:14,177 --> 00:37:15,277
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku iri.</font>

519
00:37:16,617 --> 00:37:19,947
